oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Motlow Mill on fire
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of Motlow Mill on Main Street as it is burning. Firefighters are working to extinguish the fire. People are gathered on the street to watch the fire.

oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Fires; Smoke; Fire fighting
